nHer given name, Kanade, as described by Otonashi, literally means \"Playing music\".\n\nTenshi has a variety of self-defense skills at her disposal, which she calls \"Guard Skills\".\n\n(Episode 13 spoilers)\n~! It is revealed that Kanade was the receiver of the donor heart from Otonashi. Her regret in life was her inability to thank the one who gave her the heart. After the credits, there is a short scene featuring what is assumed to be her and Otonashi reuniting in the real world !~","favourites":4139}},{"role":"BACKGROUND","node":{"id":244262,"name":{"full":"Jikogenba no Joshi"},"gender":null,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":null,"favourites":0}},{"role":"BACKGROUND","node":{"id":244272,"name":{"full":"Fushinna Otoko"},"gender":null,"image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":null,"favourites":0}},{"role":"BACKGROUND","node":{"id":244276,"name":{"full":"Danshi Seito Sawano"},"gender":"Male","image":{"large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/character/large/default.jpg"},"description":null,"favourites":0}}]}}